articles.title: Sargeant out of Baku sprint after shootout crash - ESPN - ESPN
articles.description: American driver Logan Sargeant will not take part in Saturday's sprint race at the Azerbaijan Grand Prix due to car damage sustained in the sprint shootout qualifying session earlier the same day.
